meta.description: Global submarine cable landing stations. Each facility represents a cable landing point where one or more submarine cable systems make landfall. Compatible with peeringdb_facilities.json format for merging.

schema_notes.id_range: IDs start at 100001 to avoid conflict with PeeringDB facility IDs
schema_notes.cable_systems: Array of submarine cable system names landing at this station
schema_notes.carrier_count: Number of cable systems (used for density badge coloring)
